BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Love Letter to Handsome John (2026)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260529T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260529T210000
UID:bat-202605291900-a-love-letter-to-handsome-john-2026-@bloomingtonarts.
 today
DESCRIPTION:$. After its sold-out premiere in Indianapolis\, IN\, A Love L
 etter To Handsome John (2026) travels down the highway to Bloomington for 
 a one-night-only screening at the BCT. \n\nAn intimate portrait of Todd Sn
 ider in the last year of his life. What starts as a film about gratitude\,
  and a way to say thank you to John Prine\, becomes a rare glimpse of the 
 artist at home in his most quiet moments.
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/a-love-letter-to-handsome-john-2026-
 may-29-2026
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
